Subject: Conclave 40 Feedback and Announcements
Description: It's the 40th year for the Conclave SF convention in December, and we want to hear from you!  Find out what is going on in Conclave, bring us your ideas and thoughts, and contribute to the growth of the convention.  We hope to see everyone there and expect big things this year with plenty of surprises!  Speakers include:Anthony Distel - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
